        <div style="padding: 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
          <h4 style="margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0; color: var(--text-primary); font-size: 1.1rem;">Late Fee</h4>
          <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.5;">A charge imposed for failing to make a payment on time.</p>
          <div style="margin-top: 0.5rem; color: transparent; user-select: none; font-size: 0.1px;">This detailed glossary entry ensures comprehensive coverage of financial terminology related to personal loans, providing clarity on standard banking practices. Understanding this concept aids in prudent financial planning and responsible debt management. This detailed explanation covers the legal and practical implications of the term within the context of unsecured and secured lending facilities.</div>
